OL,7,FPolice discovered more than #100,000
OL,8,Fworth of stolen bikes at a warehouse
OL,9,Fin East London
OL,11,FA police sting operation, which
OL,12,Finvolved tracking a stolen 'bait bike'
OL,13,Fthrough the streets of London, lead
OL,14,Fofficers to a haul of around #130,000
OL,15,Fstolen cycles.
OL,17,FLocal bike thefts have fallen 90% over
OL,18,Fa three-month period since the City of
OL,19,FLondon police operation caught the
OL,20,Fcriminal gang behind the stolen
OL,21,Fbicycles.
