OL,4,Cworth of stolen bikes and cut thefts
OL,5,Cby 90%
OL,7,FA bicycle fitted with a tracker was
OL,8,Fstolen in November 2020 and then
OL,9,Fpolice traced it to a warehouse in
OL,10,FEast London.
OL,12,FPolice recovered 57 other bikes at the
OL,13,Fwarehouse - being used to dismantle
OL,14,Fand dispose of the stolen bikes -
OL,15,Fvalued at around #100,000.
OL,17,FMembers of the bike stealing gang were
OL,18,Fcaught on CCTV dismantling stolen
OL,19,Fbikes at a warehouse in East London
