OL,3,CA police sting uncovered #130,000
OL,4,Cworth of stolen bikes and cut thefts
OL,5,Cby 90%
OL,7,FCCTV footage caught the gang entering
OL,8,Fthe warehouse on a daily basis and
OL,9,Fsome pulling the bikes apart.
OL,11,FThe mastermind behind the bicycle
OL,12,Fstealing ring, Louey Baldwin, was seen
OL,13,Fon the footage handing over angle
OL,14,Fgrinders, a common tool used to steal
OL,15,Fbikes, to the thieves.
OL,17,FSeven members of the gang were
OL,18,Fsentenced to prison or received a
OL,19,Fsuspended sentence, earlier in
OL,20,FFebruary.
