OL,7,FBaldwin was sentenced to two years and
OL,8,Fnine months in jail.
OL,10,FThe bike haul is thought to be the
OL,11,Fsingle largest recovered by the City
OL,12,Fof London police force.
OL,14,FAnother 21 bikes were found at the
OL,15,Fhome of Suleyman Akram, 30, who has
OL,16,Fbeen jailed for two years and six
OL,17,Fmonths for selling stolen bikes on
OL,18,Fauction websites.
