OL,7,FDuring the gang's criminal spree in
OL,8,FAugust 2020, there were 68 reported
OL,9,Fbike thefts in the City and following
OL,10,Fthe arrests the number of reported
OL,11,Fbike thefts in January 2021 fell to
OL,12,Fseven.
OL,14,FLast year, on average, there were
OL,15,Faround 19 bike thefts a month,
OL,16,Fconsiderably lower than when the gang
OL,17,Fwas operating.
