OL,7,FDetective Constable Matt Cooper, in
OL,8,Fthe Serious Organised Crime Team at
OL,9,FCity of London Police, said: "The City
OL,10,Fof London Police has been working
OL,11,Ftirelessly to catch and bring bike
OL,12,Fthieves and their handlers to justice,
OL,13,Femploying technology and innovative
OL,14,Ftechniques to limit their
OL,15,Fopportunities to commit more criminal
OL,16,Factivities.
OL,18,F"Today's sentencing shows our
OL,19,Fdedication and work to achieve this
OL,20,Foutcome.
